![Screenshot](http://rawcdn.githack.com/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/fastflix.portable/img/screenshot.png)

It needs `FFmpeg` (version 4.3 or greater required, 5.0+ recommended) under the hood for the heavy lifting, and can work with a variety of encoders.

## Package Parameters:

 - `/NoDesktopShortcut` Do not create Desktop Shortcut
 - `/NoStartMenuShortcut` Do not create Start Menu Shortcut
 
eg. `choco install -y fastflix.portable --package-parameters="/NoDesktopShortcut /NoStartMenuShortcut"`
